    "The texture information for the images is gathered by GLCM.",
    "Support Vector Machine (SVM) is then used to classify the chosen features to differentiate between benign and malignant tumors.",
    "The American Cancer Society (ACS) dataset is used to validate the suggested approach.",
    "The suggested approach outperforms all other strategies that were examined in terms of each performance metric.",
    "The suggested method successfully diagnoses melanoma with 88% accuracy."
